spec_data.Name: python2-setuptools_git
spec_data.Description:
This is a plugin for setup tools that enables Git integration.  Once
installed, Setuptools can be told to include in a module distribution
all the files tracked by git.  This is an alternative to explicit
inclusion specifications with MANIFEST.in.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 03:51:16 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Setuptools revision control system plugin for Git
